ygData.messageBody:
Ok well i am about to start my 47th eq character :)

This time i might try a bard, and i had pretty well narrowed the race down
to one of the 2 elves. I know all the pros and cons of each race, so what i
was looking for here was what they look like in plate (yes i am really that
vain :) )

I was wondering if someone knew an url that had pictures of the various
races in lambent, bronze, FS plate, imbrued etc.

I had tried the fashion table at allakhazams, but the quality of the
screenshots isnt that good


Thanks in advance


Qaelan
47 cleric
